OL,3,CExecutive faces 'cliff edge' when
OL,4,Csupport package money runs out, warns
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FThe fiscal council, which is an
OL,8,Findependent body that scrutinises how
OL,9,Fpublic money is spent in Northern
OL,10,FIreland, has conducted an assessment
OL,11,Fof the Treasury-funded settlement.
OL,13,FIt highlighted that the package
OL,14,Fincluded almost #850 million to help
OL,15,Fthe devolved Executive balance its
OL,16,Fbudget this year, including meeting
OL,17,Fthe cost of outstanding public sector
OL,18,Fpay settlements.
