OL,3,CExecutive faces 'cliff edge' when
OL,4,Csupport package money runs out, warns
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FThe council said more than #750
OL,8,Fmillion would be provided in both 2024/
OL,9,F25 and 2025/26 before there was a
OL,10,Fsharp drop-off to #320 million in 2026/
OL,11,F27.
OL,13,FThe watchdog speculated that the
OL,14,F"cliff edge" in support was presumably
OL,15,Fdesigned to encourage locally elected
OL,16,Fministers to take "decisive action" on
OL,17,Frevenue raising, budget savings and
OL,18,Fpublic service reforms.
