OL,3,CExecutive faces 'cliff edge' when
OL,4,Csupport package money runs out, warns
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FBut it said there was "no immediate
OL,8,Fevidence" of Stormont ministers taking
OL,9,Fthose steps.
OL,11,FThe Treasury has offered to write off
OL,12,Falmost #600 million of Stormont debt
OL,13,Fas part of the package.
OL,15,FBut this was conditional on the
OL,16,FExecutive raising #113 million of
OL,17,Fadditional revenue this year and
OL,18,Fproducing a plan to deliver
OL,19,Fsustainable finances.
