OL,3,CExecutive faces 'cliff edge' when
OL,4,Csupport package money runs out, warns
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FThe settlement also includes reform of
OL,8,Fthe Barnett formula for allocating
OL,9,FTreasury funds to Northern Ireland,
OL,10,Fwith funding rates for the region set
OL,11,Fat 24% above comparative rates in
OL,12,FEngland.
OL,14,FThe Government has said this will
OL,15,Freflect the "different levels of need
OL,16,Fin Northern Ireland".
OL,18,FThe fiscal council said this change to
OL,19,Fthe Barnett formula was the most
OL,20,Fsignificant longer-term feature of the
OL,21,Fsettlement.
