OL,4,Csupport package money runs out, warns
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FBut it said it remained unclear how
OL,8,Fthe new 24% mechanism would operate.
OL,10,FOffering an assessment of the overall
OL,11,Fpackage, council chairman Sir Robert
OL,12,FChote said: "The funding package
OL,13,Fshould balance the Executive's budget
OL,14,Fthis year, provide significant support
OL,15,Fover the next two years and arrest the
OL,16,F'Barnett squeeze' over the longer-term.
